rest_of_day_open:
I was in a good mood before the call and now I am in a better mood.  I think this "boost" will help me have a better week as long as it sticks with me.  

It is always nice to talk to friendly people.  We seemed to be of the same mind set, but even if we hadn't been, just having a friendly respectful conversations reminds me that there are still good people out there.
critical_positive: We both seemed to talk (giving our opinions) and asking questions (getting the other persons opinions.)  That made for a very balanced conversation.  When we didn't find a common hobby, we moved on to another hobby and continued to talk about that since we had that one in common.  Both of us put effort in to make the conversation as good as possible.
critical_negative: We probably could have taken a higher level view of each other rather than digging in to the topics we talked about.  That is why I had trouble answering some of the question previously asked in the survey.  For example, I have no idea if my conversation partner is trustworthy or honest.  I would like to think he is, but I would just be giving him the benefit of the doubt.
